import { EnvelopeIcon, PhoneIcon } from '@heroicons/react/24/outline' import {send} from 'emailjs-com' import {useState} from 'react' import Modal from './modal' import { useContext } from "react" import PortfolioContext, { PortfolioProvider, } from "../context/PortfolioContext" export default function Contact() { const { setCurrentPage, setToSend, setSubmit, submit, toSend } = useContext(PortfolioContext) const onSubmit = (e)=>{ e.preventDefault() send( 'service_ao5t6sd', 'template_kp2brax', toSend, 'UPSAdBvAIZLu7AthK' ) .then((response) => { console.log('SUCCESS!', response.status, response.text); }) .then (()=>{ setToSend({ firstName: '', lastName: '', email: '', phone: '', subject: '', message: '' }) setCurrentPage('modal') console.log(submit) }) .catch((err) => { console.log('FAILED...', err); }); } const handleChange = (e)=>{ setToSend({...toSend, [e.target.name]:e.target.value}) } return ( <> { submit ? :
